{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3764.From_Russia_With_Love", "title": "From Russia With Love", "titleComplete": "From Russia With Love (James Bond, #5)", "description": "Ian Fleming\u2019s fifth James Bond novel.James Bond is marked for death by the Soviet counterintelligence agency SMERSH in Ian Fleming\u2019s masterful spy thriller. It's the novel that President John F. Kennedy named as one of his favourite books of all time.SMERSH stands for \u2018Death to Spies\u2019 and there\u2019s no secret agent they\u2019d like to disgrace and destroy more than 007, James Bond. But ensnaring the British Secret Service\u2019s most lethal operative will require a lure so tempting even he can\u2019t resist. Enter Tatiana Romanova, a ravishing Russian spy whose \u2018defection\u2019 springs a trap designed with clockwork precision.Her mission: seduce Bond, then flee to the West on the Orient Express. Waiting in the shadows are two of Ian Fleming\u2019s most vividly drawn villains: Red Grant, SMERSH\u2019s deadliest assassin, and the sinister operations chief Rosa Klebb - five feet four inches of pure killing power.Bursting with action and intrigue, \"From Russia with Love\" is one of the best-loved books in the Bond canon, an instant classic that set the standard for sophisticated literary spycraft for decades to come.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1440169210i/3764.jpg", "genres": ["Mystery", "Spy Thriller", "Mystery Thriller", "Crime", "Fiction", "Thriller", "Adventure", "Espionage", "Audiobook", "Classics"], "asin": "0142002070", "isbn": "0142002070", "isbn13": "9780142002070", "publisher": "Penguin Books", "series": ["James Bond - Extended Series", "James Bond (Original Series)"], "author": ["Ian Fleming"], "publishDate": 1009872000000, "characters": ["James Bond"], "places": ["Istanbul"], "ratingHistogram": [581, 1715, 8726, 13957, 10455], "ratingsCount": 35434, "reviewsCount": 1604, "numPag